file_content.text: Can you believe this place? You could fit all of Tatooine in one of these high-rises.
Most of Tatooine could never afford it. They'd be in the underground, with us.
I've heard the gangs down there rule things. The Black Sun, the Exchange....
Things are bad everywhere. But this is a new life, in the Republic capital!
It's not as hot, at least. And no dust storms.
